[32m+[m[32mCover Page[m
[32m+[m[32m                        "The true meaning and significance of the Gita has always[m
[32m+[m[32mPreface to the             been passed on orally through the lineage of guru and[m
[32m+[m[32mpresent English[m
[32m+[m[32mEdition                 disciple. This cannot be understood except by the Sadguru-[m
[32m+[m[32m                            initiated sadhakas - not just scholars. Now, with the[m
[32m+[m[32mNOTES FOR[m
[32m+[m[32mTRANSLATION           permission of Sri Sri Bhagavan His Holiness [The Yogiraj Sri[m
[32m+[m[32mCLARIFICATION            Sri Lahiri Mahasay], and according to His instructions, I[m
[32m+[m[32m                        present this treasure of the supremely holy hearts of yogis,[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami                                     the Srimad Bhagavad Gita."[m
[32m+[m[32mSatyananda's[m
[32m+[m[32mPreface to the                     -- Swami Sri Yukteshvar Giriji Maharaj[m
[32m+[m[32mBengali Edition[m
