[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Sri Yukteshvar Giri ji Maharaj , and as blessings from him, to the feet of all[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Swami Maharaj's spiritual children, grandchildren and great grandchildren[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 worldwide, be it the spiritual children of the Paramhansa Yogananda, or[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 those of Swami Satyananda Giri Maharaj, or all the other equally revered[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 spiritual descendents of the Swami Maharaj.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 This 2002 English Edition belongs to no particular group, rather, it is owned[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 equally by all the spiritual descendents of the Swami Maharaj, be it East or[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 West.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 We take the dust of the feet of these great ones.[m
[32m+[m
