[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj  www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The publisher*[fn 1][m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 *The author of the commentaries, Swamiji Maharaj himself, was the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 publisher of the first edition.[fn 2][m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 [fn 1 and fn 2 - This asterisk and the explanatory footnote above is in the[m
