[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Even though powered and protected by the frightening Abhaschaitanya, it[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 seems that the side of body/ego is not formidable enough against the side of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the five elements. It also seems that the Consciousness-revealing side of the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 elements, protected by the power of the tremendous air element, will be[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 triumphant. -10-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ayaneshu cha sarveshu yathabhagamavasthitah[m
