[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Let us take our own places to fight[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Protect Bhisma everyone[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 With Bhisma fight them in the battle[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 See that no one strikes Bhisma in the back -11-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 When all of these things are experienced, a desire arises in the body/ego that[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 all of the different faculties should take their battlestations in the senses and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 protect the primary character, the terribly mighty Chidabhas. -11-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tasya samjanayan harsham kurubriddhah pitamahah[m
