[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 When this happens, then, in the white form and special path of the immersed[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yogis' bodies, with the fire element and Kutasthachaitanya - the supreme[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sound, Omkar, is experienced. -14-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 panchajanyam hrishikesho devadattam dhananjayah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 poundram dadhmou mahashankham bhimakarma brikodarah -15-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anantavijayam raja kuntiputro yudhisthirah[m
