[32m+[m[32m                                 Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I do not see any benefit in killing my own in this war[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I do not want the glory of victory and the kingdom, O Lord -31-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 What is the use of enjoying the kingdom or even life[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Krishna, the reason for the pleasures of the kingdom -32-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 They are present here ready to sacrifice life and wealth[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Teachers, uncles, sons, grandfathers -33-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Maternal uncles, father-in-law, brother-in-law and their children[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 These noble relations, Sri Madhusudhan [Krishna][m
[32m+[m[32m                                 If they wish to kill me[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I have no desire to prevent them -34-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The faculties that we need for our satisfaction, enjoyment of life and the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 embodiment of this form, those samskaras, karma, vanity/ego etc. of the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Abhaschaitanya's family as well as the other closely related faculties are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ready to die for their cause and have presented themselves here. If we[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 destroy them by this Kriya, what is the point in our happiness, enjoyment,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 body and even the necessity of living itself? Even if we die from[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 continuously serving them, we do not want to destroy them. -31, 32, 33 and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 34-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 api trailokyarajasya hetoh kim nu makrite[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 nihatyadhartarashtran nah ka priti syajjanardana -35-[m
[32m+[m
