[32m+[m[32m                                 What happiness could we possibly get, Janardana [Krishna] -35-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter1.html (23 of 29)4/18/2006 2:41:58 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Neither for this microcosmic universe of the body, nor for this world[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 manifesting in the infinite macrocosmic Universe do we want to destroy[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 these clans of the mind and ego. If they are destroyed, we have no[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 possibility of any pleasure. -35-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 papamevashrayedasman hatvaitanatatayinah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tasmannarha vayam hantum dhartarashtran sabandhavan[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 svajanam hi katham hatvah sukhinah syama madhava -36-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Killing these atatayis [criminals] of Kaurava[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Only sin will come and take our shelter[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Like our friends the Kauravas are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Therefore we cannot destroy them[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 In what way, by hurting our own[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Will we be happy, tell me Krishna -36-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Those who burn homes, poison people, take up weapons to kill, plunder and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 steal wealth, land or wives -- they are called "atatayi." There is no[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 justification needed to kill these types of people, because there is no wrong[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 in kiilling atatayis. As in -[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 agnido garadashchaiva shastrapani dhanapahah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kshetradarapahari cha shadete atatayinah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 atatayinamayantam hanyadeva vicharayan[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 natatayi badhe dosho hanturbhavati kashchan[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is true that scholars of the shastras have said this type of thing, but still, if[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 we destroy the clans of mind and ego and the faculties who are their[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 comrades, it will actually destroy us. Because -- in what way can we have[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the enjoyment of happiness if we eradicate these eternally revered faculties[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 of mind? Therefore, ddestroying these mental constructs cannot by justified[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 as a good thing. -36-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yadyapyete na pashyanti lobhopahatachetasah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kulakshayakritam dosham mitradrohe cha patakam -37-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 katham na jneyasmabhih papadasmannivartitum[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kulakshyakritam dosham prapashyadvirjanardana -38-[m
