[32m+[m[32m                                 family and friends, and are ready to destroy the experience of the five[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 elements, still, even after seeing all of the wrong of the family, how can I not[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 turn away from this harmful act (eliminating the group of ego/vanity and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 mental constructs). -37 and 38-[m
