[32m+[m[32m                                 wonderment; and some, even after studying many types of shastras and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 receiving wisdom from sages and hearing about this Brahman-Consciousness[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 again and again, still cannot understand the matter, being under the power of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 an opposing mind. -29-[m
