[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 In every body is Atman universal[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Never is He able to be killed[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Thus, for all Dhananjaya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Grief and sorrow are not proper -30-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The form of this elemental world, meaning the body - destruction of this[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 does not destroy the embodied Eternal-Consciousness. Therefore, in order to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 experience this Eternal Consciousness Para Brahman, it is not right to be[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sorrowful over the abandonment of these insignificant, dream-like and ever-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 changing things. -30-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 svadharmapi chavekshya na vikampitumaharsi[m
