[32m+[m[32m                                 Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Endlessly will people call you disgraceful[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is better for the honorable to die than have dishonor -34-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Being without Kriya and failure in Atman-dharma will be a tremendous[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 disrespect to embodiment, meaning one will suffer much. For one who is a[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 part of the Omnipotent Brahman-Consciousness, it is better to die than fail at[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Atman-dharma and eternally suffer as a slave to the elemental substances. -[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 34-[m
