[32m+[m[32m                                 perfection through Kriya, reduces this entire elemental world into a game of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 dolls. Therefore, it is one's duty to resolutely perform Kriya with all-out[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 effort in the power of the fire element. -37-[m
