[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 In the end is of no good, for the moment satisfying[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Ignorant persons are captivated by those words[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Saying realization comes from studying that[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 And they say that there is nothing else beside this[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Filled with desires, their craving minds[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Heaven, the land of gods, they deem as the highest[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 And are reborn according to the karma they followed[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The karma that keeps them in greed and pleasures of senses[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The teachings for the attainment of such, they call the best -42 and 43-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Those whose minds are on karmakanda [rituals] and words of the Vedas[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Only addicted to pleasure, always, they are[m
