[32m+[m[32m                                 etc. under complete control and reside separately from them as the Self, and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 those who realize the Consciousness pervading the Universe into Brahman[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter5.html (3 of 16)4/18/2006 2:42:04 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Itself to be undifferentiated from the Atman-Consciousness in oneself --[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 they, even though they perform all kinds of karma for the maintenance of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 physical life, are unattached to any of their resuults; they are not enmeshed in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 them. -7-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 naiva kinchit karomiti yuktomanyata tattvavit[m
