[32m+[m[32m                                   oneself, no one has to partake in the results of such work. Understanding[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter5.html (4 of 16)4/18/2006 2:42:04 PM[m
