[32m+[m[32m                                 karma equally in their minds and reside happily in the bodily city of nine[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 doors -- mouth, dual openings of the nose, dual openings of the eyes, dual[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 openings of the ears, and the urinary and excretory openiings. Such a being[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 as Self is not engaged in any karma, and nor does he cause the body and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 senses to become engaged in any work. -13-[m
[32m+[m
