[32m+[m[32m                                 Self does not perform any work. Also, It does not cause the body, mind,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 intellect and the senses etc. to be engaged in any work, nor does It desire to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 enjoy the fruits of any karma. All work is done by nature in ignorance. -14-[m
[32m+[m
