[32m+[m[32m                                 duhkhamevasarvavivekinah - Sadhanapada - no. 15-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 This has been clearly explained in the commentary to slokas 16 and 17 of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 this chapter. It is unnecessary to mention it further here. Thus, only the sutra[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 is being stated. -22-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 shaknotihaiva yah sodhum prak sharira vimokshanat[m
