[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 enjoyment of material things and have experienced Atman-Consciousness in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the form of Light within, and those who engage in the performance of Kriya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with inner joy and practice poise at the end of Kriya -- those Kriyavan[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sadhakas by this type of Kriya eradicate all samskaras and attain the state of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 asamprajnata samadhi. Havinng attained the highest state of samadhi in this[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 way, finally they merge into that Brahman-Substance and realize[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Kaivalyapada. About this, it is written thus in Patanjal philosophy: as in -[m
