[32m+[m[32m                                 viramapratyayabhyasapurvah samskarasheshohanyah - Samadhipada - no.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 18 -[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 By the practice of the mind/intellect-ceasing poise, all samskaras are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 eradicated and one can attain asamprajnatavastha, the highest state of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 samadhi. -24-[m
