[32m+[m[32m                                 aforementioned yogakriya have destroyed ignorance, or unawareness, and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 thereby who experience the Consciousness-Self, by which who are united[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with the Self and perceive the oneness of things - up to the Ultimate - and are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 always present for works of the good -- they are the ones who are merged in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 that Brahman-Substance. -25-[m
[32m+[m
