[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                      Poetically:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mErosion of sins in rajoguna, tranquil becomes the mind[m
[32m+[m[32mIn that yoga is found the eternal happiness -27-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCommentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBy the practice of such withdrawal of the senses, when the mind attains tranquility and the[m
[32m+[m[32mpurity of the sattvic condition by having become free of the scattered-ness arising from[m
[32m+[m[32mrajoguna and the sleepy, drowsy/laziness arising from tamoguna, sadhakas become able to[m
[32m+[m[32mlive in Supreme Bliss. -27-[m
[32m+[m
