[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBy the continuous and gradual practice of the restful poise of the aforementioned method[m
[32m+[m[32mas received from Sadguru, and thereby being able to remain one with Atman-[m
[32m+[m[32mConsciousness, sadhakas experience all of the created Cosmos up to the Ultimate as the[m
[32m+[m[32mform of that Infinite Brahman-Consciousness and effortlessly attain the beyond-immense[m
[32m+[m[32mBliss of Brahman. -28-[m
[32m+[m
