[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIn this way the sadhakas established in Consciousness-Self, experiencing that Infinite[m
[32m+[m[32mConsciousness as completely in everything in the Universe, experience the subsistence of[m
[32m+[m[32mall things in this Immovable Brahman-infused world as of the Consciousness-Self and in[m
[32m+[m[32mthe Consciousness-Self. -29-[m
