[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCommentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThose who in this way experience the existence of all created things of the world as[m
[32m+[m[32mAtman-Consciousness's and in Atman-Consciousness, those eternally merged sadhakas'[m
[32m+[m[32mconsciousnesses are always in an awakened state. They are never outside of[m
[32m+[m[32mConsciousness, meaning they are never "un-"conscious. They live ever-awakened. -30-[m
[32m+[m
