[32m+[m[32mHe becomes enraptured with Me -31-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCommentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThose who by Sadguru's instructions take refuge in the immovable, this Brahman-[m
[32m+[m[32membodied-in-all elements, Universe-pervading Consciousness and reside in that, they, no[m
[32m+[m[32mmatter where they are in whatever way they are, are always residing in the Consciousness-[m
[32m+[m[32mState. Nothing of creation is able to make them unconscious. -31-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32matmoupamyena sarvatra samam pashyati yoharjuna[m
