[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The ignorant, indiscriminating, evil-doing, sin-enmeshed and base human[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 beings, having been stupefied by the sattva-, raja- and tamoguna-filled,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 supernatural-power-endowed Maya, acquire many types of demonic qualities[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 such as egotism etc. and are thus bound by ego-self-consciousness. Although[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 this three-guna-filled, supernatural-power-endowed Maya is extremely[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter7.html (8 of 16)4/18/2006 2:42:07 PM[m
