[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 difficult to traverse, those who have taken up the path of Consciousness and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 who are performing the Sadguru-given Kriya are able to easily cross beyond[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 this Maya and experience that Eternal, Bliss-of-Knowledge Form of Atman-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Consciousness. -14 and 15-[m
