[32m+[m[32m                                   That is who is called the realized liberated devotee[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Beloved to devotees, I am greatest to them[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   They have no one more dear to them[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   My devotees are all the highest[m
