[32m+[m[32m                                 the Vedas, such sadhakas take up many types of processes such as living[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with Guru etc., along with brahmacharya, and giving up the body thereafter,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 they attain Ecstatic Union. That matter of attaining Nirvana is being[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 explained in a summarized manner. -11-[m
