[32m+[m[32m                                        CHAPTER ELEVEN[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 VISHVARUPADARSHANAYOGA[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mHome                             Arjuna said:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 madanugrahaya paramam guhyamadhyatmasamjnitam[m
[32m+[m[32mCover Page                       yat tvayoktam vachastena mohohyam vigato mama -1-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32mPreface to the                   It is being experienced in the fire element of the body: By Your speaking out[m
[32m+[m[32mpresent English                  of mercy about the secret spirituality, my delusion has gone. -1-[m
[32m+[m[32mEdition[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhavapyayou hi bhutanam shrutou vistarasho maya[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami                            tattvah kamalapatraksha mahatmyamapi chavyayam -2-[m
[32m+[m[32mSatyananda's                     Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32mPreface to the                   I listened much about the power of the five elements and the Indestructible.[m
[32m+[m[32mBengali Edition                  -2-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIntroduction                     evametad yathattha tvamatmanam parameshvara[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drashtumicchami te rupamaishvaram purushottama -3-[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 1                        Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 2                        This Atman is Itself the Supreme God. The longing to see the Cosmic Form[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 3                        of the Lord. -3-[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 4[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 5                        manyase yadi tacchakyam maya drashtumiti prabho[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 6                        yogeshvara tato me tvam darshayatmanamavyayam -4-[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 7[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 8[m
[32m+[m[32mChapter 9[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (1 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 10                  Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 11                  If You think that I am worthy of seeing, then show me the Eternal Form. -4-[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 12[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 13                  Sri Bhagavan said:[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 14                  pashya me partha rupanishatashohtha sahasrashah[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 15                  nanavidhani divyani nanavarnakritini cha -5-[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 16                  Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 17                  It is being experienced via Kutastha: Look at My hundreds of thousands of[m
[32m+[m[32m     Chapter 18                  Forms, innumerable types of things, innumerable depictions. -5-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyatityan vasun rudranashvinou marutastatha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bahunyadrishtapurvani pashyashcharyani bharata -6-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Surya, Vasu, Rudra, Ashvini, Marut, all these you have seen. Behold all the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 wonders. -6-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ihaikestham jagat kritsnam pashyadya sacharacharam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 mama dehe gudakesha yacchanyad drashtumicchasi -7-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The One Brahman is within all creation, and you are longing to see this in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 your own body. -7-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 na tu mam shakyate drashtumanenaiva svachakshusha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 divyam dadami te chakshu pashya me yogamaishvaram -8-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 These eyes are not capable of seeing; I am revealing you the divine eye,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 meaning Kutastha, by which you can see my Divine Form. -8-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Sanjay said:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   evamukta tato rajan mahayogeshvaro harih[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   darshayamasa parthaya paramam rupamaishvaram -9-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   It is being experienced by the subtle perception of the mind: In this way, he[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (2 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 [Arjuna] began to see the Form of God via Kutastha. -9-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anekavaktranayanamanekadbhutadarshanam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anekadivyabharanam divyanekodyatayudham -10-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Many mouths, meaning - there are many people in front of Kutastha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 [wearing] numerous ornaments and holding numerous weapons. -10-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 divyamalyambaradharam divyagandhanulepanam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sarvashcharyamayam devamanantam vishvatomukham -11-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 [Arjuna] began to see wondrous bodies - and the Form in Space adorned[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with divine garlands, divine clothing and [emanating] divine perfume - and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 continued to see more forms. -11-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 divi suryasahasrasya bhaved yugapadutthita[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yadi bhah sadrishi syadbasastasya mahatmahah -12-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 In space, even greater than the splendor of thousands of suns at the time of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the Great Dissolution. -12-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tatraikastham jagat kritsnam pravibhaktamanekadha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 apashyaddevadevasya sharire pandavastada -13-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 He continued to see many different worlds in that place, separately and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 together in the bodies of the Pandavas. -13-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tatah sa vismayavishto hrishtaroma dhananjayah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pranamya shirasa devam kritanjalirabhashata -14-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Awestruck and with hairs standing on end, he [Arjuna] bowed prayerfully[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with folded hands. -14-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Arjuna said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (3 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyami devam stava devadehe[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sarvamstatha bhutavisheshasamghan[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 brahmanamisham kamalasanastham[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 rishimshcha sarvanuragamshcha divyan -15-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The fire energy of the body is saying: I see all phenomena in Your Body -[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Brahma, Vishnu, Maheshvara - all in the form of revelatory space. -15-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anekabahudaravaktranetram[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyami tvam sarvatohnantarupam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 nantam na madyam na punastavadim[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyami vishveshvara vishvarupam -16-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Many arms, abdomens, Infinite Form - all in front [of me]. There is no[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 beginning, middle, end. You are the Universal Form. -16-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kiritinam gadinam chakrinancha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tejorashim sarvato diptimantam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyami tvam durnirikshyam samantad[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 diptanalarkadyurtimaprameyam -17-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Wearing a crown and holding a mace, immense energy from the spinning[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 discus, brilliant radiance all over - [so much that] it is difficult to look at[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You. There is no light even beyond fire and sun that can even come close to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 measuring up. -17-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamaksharam paramam veditavyam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamasya vishvasya param nidhanam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamavyayah shashvatadharmagopta[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 satatanastvam purusho mato me -18-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are the Indestructible, the Supreme to be realized, the resort of the entire[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Cosmos and samsara. You are the Immortal, Eternal Absolute, and the Secret[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Dharma - Primordial Person. -18-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anadimadhyantamanantaviryam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anantabahum shashisuryanetram[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (4 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pashyami tvaam diptahutashavaktram[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 svatejasa vishvamidam tapantam -19-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Without beginning, middle, end, the Eternal Cause, eyes of moon and sun,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 with fiery blaze coming from Your mouths - scorching the inflamed[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 manifested Cosmos and samsara. -19-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 dyavaprithivivyoridamantaram hi[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vyaptam tvayaikena dishashashcha sarvah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtvadbhutam rupamugram tavedam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 lokatrayam pravyathitam mahatman -20-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Heaven, earth, space in all of which the fire pervades and in all directions -[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the three worlds and myself are in tremendous fear seeing this incredible and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 intense form of Yours - the three worlds - meaning from the foot to the navel[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 - the underworld; the navel to the throat - the mortal world; and the throat to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the head - heavenly world. -20-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ami hi tvaam surasamgha vishanti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kechidbhitah pranjalayo grinanti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 svastityuktva maharshisiddhasamghah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 stuvantitvaam stutibhi pushkalabhih -21-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The gods are singing Your praises and hailing You. The perfected sages are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 also singing Your praises abundantly. -21-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 rudraditya vasavo ye cha sadhya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vishvehshvinou marutashchoshmapashcha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 gandharvayakshasurasiddhasamgha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vikshante tvaam vismitashchaiva sarve -22-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Rudras, Adityas, Sadhus, Ashvins, Maruts, Gandharvas, Yakshas, Suras,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Siddhas -- all are beholding You. -22-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 rupam mahat te bahuvaktranetram[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 mahabaho bahubahurupadam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bahudaram bahudamshtrakaralam[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (5 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtva lokah pravythitastathaham -23-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 nabhah sprisham diptamanekavarnam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vyattananam diptavishalanetram[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtva hi tvaam pravyathitantaratma[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 dhritim na vindami shamancha vishno -24-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 The immensely radiant Form, many mouths, eyes, arms, bellies, legs, teeth --[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 beholding which the many great beings and myself have become terrified.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Seeing the intense effulgence and huge eyes, my mind cannot hold itself. -[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 23 and 24-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 damshtrakaralani cha te mukhani[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtaiva kalanalasannibhani[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 disho na jane na labhe cha sharma[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 prasida devesha jagannivasa -25-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 All sense of direction is lost in the Fire of the Light. -25-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ami cha tvaam dhritarashtrasya putrah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sarvesahaivavanipalasamghaih[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhishmo dronoh sutaputrastathasou[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sahasmadiyairapi yodhamukhyaih -26-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 All the sons of Dhritarashtra, Bhishma, Drona, Karna - all are entering into[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Your mouth. -26-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vaktrani te tvaramana vishanti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 damshtrakaralani bhayanakani[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kechidvilagna dashanantareshu[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 samdrishyante churnitairuttamangaih -27-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Stuck and hanging in the large teeth in the mouths, You are even crunching[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 and chewing the heads of some. -27-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yatha nadinam bahavohmbuvegah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 samudramevabhimukha dravanti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tatha tavami naralokavira[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (6 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vishanti vaktranyabhivijvalanti -28-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 As all rivers fall into the sea, in that way are all valiant warriors falling into[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Your mouths. -28-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yatha pradiptam jvalanam patanga[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vishanti nashaya samriddha vegah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tathaiva nashaya vishanti loka-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 stavapi vaktrani samriddhavegah -29-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 As moths die in the flame of a lamp, in that way all soldiers and falling into[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the torrent. -29-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 lelihyase grasamanah samasta-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 llokan samagran vadanairjvaladbhih[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tejobhirapurya jagat samagram[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhasastavograh pratapanti vishno -30-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Blazing, licking tongue is seen in the Face, and terribly intense, fiery Light.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 -30-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 akhyahi me ko bhavanugrarupo[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 namohstute devavara prasida[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vijnatumicchami bhavantamadyam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 na hi prajanami tava pravrittim -31-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Who are You? I bow down to You. O Lord of lords, I do not know from[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 where You begin or Your intention. -31-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Sri Bhagavan said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kalohsmi lokakshyakrit pravriddho[m
