[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced via Kutastha: Behold My Form as Time/Death, the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Lord of Destruction. All of the valiant ones are being dissolved in Me. -32-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tasmat tvamuttishtha yasho labhasva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 jitva shatrun bhunkshva rajyam samriddham[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 mayaivaite nihatah purvameva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 nimittamatra bhava savyasachin -33-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 For this reason, get up and gain victory; enjoy the prosperity of the kingdom.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I have already killed everyone. You are just an excuse [for that to happen].[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 (In this way, it is first experienced here that all those fears and trials have[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 already been ended; they are only delusions.) -33-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 dronancha bhishmancha jayadrathancha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 karnam tathannyanapi yodhaviran[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 maya hatam stvam jahi ma vyathishtha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yudhyasva jetasi rane sapatnan -34-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Drona, Bhishma, Jayadratha, Karna, and all the great warriors -- I have killed[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 them all, along with their wives. -34-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Sanjay said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 etacchrutva vachanam keshavasya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kritanjalirvepamanah kiriti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 namaskritva bhuya evaha krishnam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sagadagadam bhitabhitah pranamya -35-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced in the subtle perception: in this way it is experienced[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 in the Kutastha that prostration is happening over and over again with fear[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 and overwhelmed heart choked with feeling. -35-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Arjuna said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   stane hrishikesha tava prakirtya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   jagat prahyashyatyanurajyate cha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   rakshamsi bhitani disho dravanti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   sarve namasyanti cha siddhasamghah -36-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (8 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced in the energy of the body: All are terrified by Your[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Light. All directions are being dissolved, and even perfected beings are as if[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 afraid, it seems. -36-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kasmaccha te na nameran mahatman[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 gariyase brahmanohpyadikartre[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ananta devesha jagannivasa[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamaksharam sadasat tat param yat -37-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are the God of gods. You are the abode [of all], beyond truth and the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 world. -37-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamadidevah purushah purana-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 stvamasya vishvasya para nidhanam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vettasi vedyancha parancha dhama[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvaya tatam vishvamantarupa -38-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are the Primordial God. You are the Most Ancient Person, the Greatest[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 of all existence. You are the foundation of all. You are that which is to be[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 known, and You make Yourself known. You are that which should be known[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 and You are the Supreme. You are the Infinite Existence. -38-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vayuryamohgnirvarunah shashankah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 prajapatistvam prapitamahashcha[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 namo namastehstu sahasrakritvah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 punashcha bhuyohpi namo namaste -39-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are wind, death, fire, the ruler of the sea, the moon, Brahma [the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 creator], the grandfather. I prostrate to You thousands and thousands of[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 times. Again and again I give my salutations to You. -39-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 namah purastadatha prishthataste[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 namohstu te sarvata eva sarva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 anantaviryamita vikramastvam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sarvam samapnoshi tatohsi sarvah -40-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (9 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I bow to Your front. I bow to Your back. I bow to You and I bow to all who[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 are Yours [alt: all that is Yours]. Infinite valor, infinite might -- all are You.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 -40-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sakheti matva prasabham yaduktam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 he krishna he yadava he sakheti[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ajanata mahimanam tavedam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 maya pramadat pranayena vapi -41-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 As a friend I have called You - O Krishna, O Yadava, O friend - without[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 knowing this magnificence, I have addressed You out of carelessness and[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 affection. -41-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 yacchavahasarthamasatkritohsi[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 viharashayasanabhojaneshu[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ekohthavapyachyuta tatsamaksham[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tat kshamaye tvamahamaprameyam -42-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 In whatever way I may have disrespected You - in playfulness, while sitting,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 while at meals, while lying down - please forgive all of that. -42-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 pitasi lokasya characharasya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tvamasya pujyashcha gururgariyan[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 na tvatsamohstyabhyadhikah kutohnyo[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 lokatrayehpyapratimaprabhavah -43-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are the Father. In the world of mobile and immobile, You are the One to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 be worshipped and the Guru of gurus. There is no one equal to You and no[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 one can be more than You in these three worlds. -43-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   tasmat pranamya pranidhaya kayam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   prasadaye tvamahamishamidyam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   piteva putrasya sakheva sakhyuh[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   priyah priyayarhasi deva sodhum -44-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Because of that, I fully prostrate to You. You are the Supreme.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   [IMPORTANT NOTE: From this point in sloka 11:44 through sloka 11:49,[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (10 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 there seems to have been an editing error in the published Bengali printing[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 transcribed from the original handwritten text. The printed commentaries are[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 displaced - they do not concord with the appropriate slokas from this point in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 11:44 through 11:49. Upon examination, it can be found that by aligning the[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 commentaries correctly with their respective slokas, there should have been[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 no commentary for sloka 11:49 in the published Bengali print. This[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 translation presents the material in the manner in which the commentaries[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 correspond accurately to their respective slokas and indicates that there is in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 actuality no commentary for sloka 11:49 in the published Bengali print. No[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 liberties have been taken with the actual translation of the Bengali. The[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 commentaries have been merely lined up. The reader is asked to understand[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 that this part of the Gita, through the conclusion of the book, was found as a[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 set of! handwritten notes by Swami Sriyukteshvar Giri Maharaj and was not[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 intended for publishing, and mistakes such as these by the printer could have[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 occurred due to the difficulty in transferring the original handwritten text to[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the printed medium.][m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 You are father, son, friend, beloved, god. -44-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 adrishtapurvam hrishitohsmi drishtva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhayena cha pravyathitam mano me[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tadeva me darshaya deva rupam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 prasida devesha jagannivasa -45-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I have never seen this Form of Yours, and because of this, there is fear in my[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 mind. Therefore, [please] show me Your Form. -45-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 kiritnam gadinam chakrahasta-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 micchami tam drashtumaham tathaiva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tenaiva rupena chaturbhujena[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sahasrabaho bhava vishvamurte -46-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 I want to now see Your crowned, mace-bearing, discus-bearing Form, from[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 which You have assumed this Universal Form. -46-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Sri Bhagavan said:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   maya prasannena tavarjunedam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   rupam param darshitamatmayogat[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   tejomayam vishvamanantamadyam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   yanme tvadanyena na drishtapurvam -47-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                   Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (11 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced via Kutastha: Being pleased, I have revealed to you in[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 the Yoga of Atman this Powerful, Universal, Infinite, Beginningless Form --[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 that which you have never seen. -47-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 na vedayajnadhyayanairna danai-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 rna cha kriyabhirna tapobhurugraih[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 evam rupah shakya aham nriloke[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drashtum tvadanyena kurupravira -48-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 No one can be witness to that terribly intense Form [even by the study or[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 practice of] Veda, yajna, charity, works or austerities. -48-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ma te vyatha macha vimudhabhavo[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtva rupam ghoramidringmamedam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 vyapetabhuh pritamanah punastam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 tadeva me rupamidam prapashya -49-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 [THERE IS NO COMMENTARY IN THE PUBLISHED BENGALI[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 PRINTING FOR SLOKA 11:49. PLEASE SEE NOTE WITHIN THE[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 COMMENTARY SECTION OF SLOKA 11:44.][m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Sanjay said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ityarjunam vasudevastathoktva[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 svakam rupam darshayamasabhuyah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 ashvasayamasa cha bhitamenam[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhutva punah soumyavapurmahatma -50-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced in the subtle perception: Kutastha again assumed His[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Form. -50-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Arjuna said:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 drishtedam manusham rupam tava soumyam janardana[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 idanimasmi samvrittah sachetah prakritim gatah -51-[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced in the energy of the body: Seeing this human form,[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfile:///C|/Yoga%20Niketan/sriyukteshvargita/chapter11.html (12 of 14)4/18/2006 2:42:11 PM[m
[32m+[m[32mSwami Sriyukteswar Giri Maharaj        www.yoganiketan.net[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 my mind became composed and satisfied, and I returned to my natural state.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 -51-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Sri Bhagavan said:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 sudurdarshamidam rupam drishtavanasi yanmama[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 deva apyasya rupasya nityam darshanakankhinah -52-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 It is being experienced via Kutastha: No one is able to witness this Form.[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Even gods desire to see this Form. -52-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 naham vedairna tapasa na danena na chejyaya[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 shakya evamvidho drashtum drishtavanasi mam yatha -53-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Not by Vedas, not by austerities, not by charity, not by yajna can this Form[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 be seen -- which you have seen. -53-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 bhaktya tvananyaya shakyah ahamevam vidhoharjuna[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 jnatum drashtumcha praveshtumcha parantapa -54-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 By single-minded devotion can this Form be seen. -54-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 matkarmakrinmatparamo madbhaktah sangavarjitah[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 nirvairah sarvabhuteshu yah sa mameti pandava -55-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Commentary:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Do My work, meaning - do Kriya. Remain always in Me. Be devoted to Me[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 without desire. Do not make enmity with anyone. If this is done, you will get[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Me. -55-[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m                                 Thus ends the eleventh chapter named "Vishvarupadarshanayoga."[m
